for running the task scrips please enter the following command 

basicCheck.sh <current dir(including the /basicCheck.sh> <file.exe>

*for creating an prexecut file please enter the following command 

g++ <prg.cpp> -o <any.exe>

*make sure you have in your currend dir the "makefile" for creating the executable file

*make sure you have only one main included cpp program in the current dir
